<br>
With the new planar AA's allowing you to basically add 30 points to each of your BASE resists, it gets kind of tempting.<br>
<br>
But, as always with melees and AAs, since we can't bounce out an AA every 20 minutes like CoD chanters can, we tend to go in real specific AA paths, to make the best use of the AAs we do finally get.<br>
<br>
I don't know too many warriors or monks besides me that have even considered getting the resist AAs until after everything else defense/HP wise AND DPS/offense wise is done and out of the way.<br>
<br>
And by that time, your resists are usually right where they need to be.<br>
<br>
On the FLIP SIDE though, I've heard there really is no point of diminishing returns for resists. Soooo ... maybe they're not too bad to work on after all.<br>
<br>
I'd be interested in hearing from anyone who considered getting the resist AAs before, say, Physical Enhancement or completing Combat Agility.<br>
<br>
-Wubao <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showPrevMessage?topicID=5158.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showNextMessage?topicID=5158.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5158.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=5158.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.threadControl?topicID=5158.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5158.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5158.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cell